RULES OF THE GAME

Apr 26, 2024
Apr 26, 2024

Inception at Hackathon

The journey begins with the creative inception of our collection at the esteemed hackathon hosted by tokenforge.gg. Here, talented developers, artists, and blockchain enthusiasts converge to craft the first generation of our unique NFTs. This pivotal event lays the foundation for our game, with each collectible being not just a work of art but a cornerstone of the gameplay experience that awaits.

Apr 30, 2024
Apr 30, 2024

Funding Approval and AC-DAO Grant Receipt

We are thrilled to announce a significant milestone in our journey the approval of our project's budget by the AC-DAO in NDC for May. This approval includes a substantial grant that will be instrumental in advancing our project's development. The grant not only provides financial backing but also validates our vision and the potential impact of our game within the community. This stage marks a pivotal point in our roadmap, setting the foundation for accelerated growth and innovation. AC-DAO: NDC May Budget Application.

Stage 1
Stage 1

Beta Game Launch

Following the momentum of our inaugural collection, we proudly announce the beta launch of our game. This stage allows players to not only witness the stunning visuals and intricate designs of their acquired NFTs but to actively engage with them in a rich, interactive gaming environment. The beta version serves as a testbed for refinement, where community feedback is paramount to enhancing the gaming experience.

Stage 2
Stage 2

Tournament Organization

With the game's mechanics refined and the communitys strategies emerging, we step into the competitive arena with our first official tournament. This event will not only showcase the prowess and skill of our top players but will also highlight the strategic depth of our game. Participants will battle for glory, prizes, and the chance to cement their names in the games burgeoning history.

Stage 3
Stage 3

Game Evolution and NFT Expansion

Building on the excitement of the tournament, we move forward to the next game version, introducing new layers of complexity and opportunities. This update expands the capabilities and utilities of our NFTs, ensuring that they remain at the cutting edge of both aesthetic value and in-game functionality. This stage represents our commitment to growth and the continuous evolution of our gaming ecosystem.
